snippet.title: Morbid: A True Crime Podcast | William Bonin  The Freeway Killer  Part 2
snippet.description:
Morbid: A True Crime Podcast | William Bonin  The Freeway Killer  Part 2
Just when you survived the brutality of part one, we’ve got part two coming right at ya. William Bonin is still up to no good, traipsing around the streets of CA in his murder van with his disgusting accomplices. Luckily in this part we’ll get into how William was caught, talk about the trial and how everyone turned on each other and the finality of this case!
We also discuss a current missing kids case from Tennessee. 3 year old Noah Clare and 16 year old Amber Clare were abducted by family member Jake Clare In Tennessee and Kentucky. The car he was driving them in was abandoned in San Clemente California.
